        Anda fokus pada riset dan pengembangan konten.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Overlapping Cards Layout -->
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Pain Points Card (Behind/Receded) -->
      <div
        class="bg-slate-100/80 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200/50 max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-0"
      >
        <h3
          class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
        >
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-200/80 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span>Tantangan Self-Managed</span>
        </h3>

        <!-- Compact horizontal list for pain points -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
            <span class="opacity-50 grayscale text-base">ğŸ’³</span>
            <span>Kurs USD</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
            <span class="opacity-50 grayscale text-base">âš™ï¸</span>
            <span>Setup Manual</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">
